comment.string: "Model that tests the basic element that is used to built heat exchanger models"
"Model to compute the water vapor pressure at the dew point"
"Model to convert water vapor pressure into humidity ratio"

primarys.simple_primary:
"

This test circulates air in a loop. Air has a constant inlet temperature into the coil. The model verifies that the air will be dehumidified to the dewpoint of the coil surface.
